c: 3
v: 37
t: "So her Lord (Allah) accepted her with goodly acceptance. He made her grow in a good manner and put her under the care of Zakariya (Zachariya). Every time he entered Al-Mihrab to (visit) her, he found her supplied with sustenance. He said: \"O Maryam (Mary)! From where have you got this?\" She said, \"This is from Allah.\" Verily, Allah provides sustenance to whom He wills, without limit"